reviews.review_msg: Was pregnant, so she only taught the lecture portion. Candace was a great TA and she gave a lot of feedback on the writing assignments. Tests were average in difficulty and requires knowledge and examples from both lecture and course material.

Great prof very nice and knew her stuff, little trouble between TA and prof. communication. wouldnt recommend this class if you dont like writing or lots of work  but the lectures are engaging and intersting course material
